{
  "stem": "1173.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to go every day to work in the woods, cutting woods, and didn't-- we get our 800 grams of bread, and some fish soup, and that, that, that was it.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "However, my parents-- I don't know how, but they sent to me three packages, which helped a lot because I could trade some shoes and boots, and some other stuff for food.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that camp, I don't remember exactly how long we were there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There, there was no attempt to escape, because it was-- the nearest village or nearest town was probably a hundred of kilometers or miles away, and through woods.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nobody even tried. 19-- I don't know exactly the year, but just when the war started between the Russian and the German, which was I think '41, they took us out of the camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by trains, they send us on the way to Asia, to Uzbekistan and Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On the way, I remember, I got sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I got typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they took me off the train, and I stayed in a hospital in Saratov, quite a big city in Russia, not far from Stalingrad, which was the very famous.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was in the hospital about three or four weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And after that, they put me in another transport, which was going to Asia, to Kazakhstan, Uzbekistan.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was in Tashkent for a couple of days, and then they shipped us to, to Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Tashkent is in Uzbekistan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They shipped us to Kazakhstan, few hundred miles away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The name of the town was Leger L-E-G-E-R.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That was a small town where they were looking for oil.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then we worked there on the-- in the-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Looking for oil?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Drilling for oil.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
